Class GreenAssignment

java.lang.Object
model.Assignment
model.GreenAssignment
public class GreenAssignment extends Assignment
Represents a green assignment with completion status, times completed, and a due date. Extends the abstract Assignment class. author SEP Group 1
Version:
1.0 (28/11-2025)
